Hello! Thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides, your friendly local bowling alley. My name is Alex. How can I assist you today?

Hi Alex! I'm calling about a billing issue I encountered. My name is Jamie.

Nice to meet you, Jamie! Could you please tell me how I can help with your billing issue?

Sure, I noticed an extra charge on my bill from my last visit, and I wanted to clarify what it was for.

I see. Let me take a look into that for you. Can I have your billing account number? It's the one that starts with a five.

Yes, it's five six seven eight.

Great, thank you. Also, can I confirm the last four digits of the phone number associated with your account for verification purposes?

Sure, the last four digits are nine zero two one.

Thank you, Jamie. I have found your account. It looks like the extra charge was for some snacks from the vending machine. Does that sound right?

Oh, yes, I forgot about that. Thanks for clarifying!

You're welcome! Is there anything else I can help you with today?

Nope, that was all. Thanks for your help, Alex!

You’re welcome, Jamie. Thank you for your time, and have a great day!
